{#
name: Daily Report
description: Generate daily reports from data sources with configurable sections and recipients
tags: [report, daily, aggregation]
parameters:
  - name: skill_name
    type: str
    description: Skill display name
    required: true
  - name: skill_description
    type: str
    description: Brief description of daily report purpose
    required: true
  - name: data_sources
    type: str
    description: Comma-separated data sources (e.g. db:sales, api:metrics, logs)
    required: true
  - name: report_sections
    type: str
    description: Comma-separated section names (e.g. summary, trends, issues)
    required: true
  - name: recipients
    type: str
    description: Comma-separated recipient channels (e.g. email, slack, webhook)
    required: true
examples:
  - "Daily sales and inventory report"
  - "Ops daily summary with incident highlights"
#}
---
name: {{ skill_name | kebab_case }}
description: {{ skill_description }}
metadata:
  author: owlclaw
  version: "1.0"
owlclaw:
  spec_version: "1.0"
  task_type: report
---
# {{ skill_name }} — 使用指南

## 目标

{{ skill_description }}

## 报告配置

- 数据源：{{ data_sources }}
- 章节：{{ report_sections }}
- 接收方：{{ recipients }}

## 生成逻辑

1. 从 data_sources 拉取数据
2. 按 report_sections 组织内容
3. 生成结构化日报
4. 推送到 recipients 对应通道

## 注意事项

- 建议固定每日触发时间（如 9:00）
- report_sections 顺序影响输出结构
- recipients 需预先配置
